a virtual Beth Harmon at different ages and stages of her chess career. 

 <> 

PLAY CHESS WITH
 BETH HARMON 
 <> 




At what age can you beat the powerful player from the popular series The 
Queen’s Gambit? 

Let’s Play! <https://www.chess.com/play/computer?bot=Beth8-bot> 


Meet a few of the Beth Harmon personalities you can challenge to a match! 



Beth (8) (800) 
Beth has just started playing chess. She still falls for traps and doesn’t see 
certain types of tactics, but she is improving quickly! Can you beat her before 
she becomes too strong? 





Beth (9) (1200) 
Beth has improved under the tutelage of Mr. Shaibel. She has started studying 
her openings and has a basic understanding of tactics and checkmates. Can you 
compete? 





Beth (10) (1600) 
Beth is a strong club player now, capable of taking on a room full of high 
school players in a simultaneous exhibition. Can you survive against this chess 
prodigy? 





Beth (17) (2400) 
Beth is playing at the strength of an International Master. She has proven 
herself at the national level and is ready for an international stage. Are you 
ready? 





Beth (22) (2700) 
Beth has been dreaming of playing for the world championship for two years, 
and aspires to be the youngest World Chess Champion ever. Do you dare to stand 
in her way? 



Are you up for the challenge? 

